snippet.textDisplay: This is the expectation I had been having from Coke Studio Bangla since its inception! Coke Studio Bangla needed to gain traction in the early years with tried and true Bangla styles of music. But this? This is Coke Studio Bangla finally gaining courage to spread her wings and fly towards a destination yet undiscovered. This particular production has set the creative standard. The singers, the lyrics, the production value - top notch. Hats off!
